result.name: Siu Hei Court

reviews.text: nice environment, close to the ocean walk
Ok

This development has 5 residential buildings under Home Ownership Scheme established by Hong Kong Housing Authority over 30 years.  The spaces between each building are large which are used to be playgrounds and gardens.  Many developments usually occupied all the spaces for residential bulidings or paid facilities, especially the new development.  The flats are in 2 types only, i.e. with one bedroom and two bedrooms.  The saleable area is 90% of the gross area.  Dining room is large but bedroom(s) is/are small.
It is very nice place and all people living in here are very well.
Nice place to stay if you are looking for a cheaper rent.
